               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18040516-14-cd75" type="crimeDate">30th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18040516-14-off74 t18040516-14-cd75"></join>, three quarters of a pound weight of tobacco
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18040516-14-victim161" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Pearson
                  <interp inst="t18040516-14-victim161" type="surname" value="Pearson"></interp>
